text: Peter Aho (born 2 March 2003) is a Nigerian cricketer. He played 16 Twenty20 Internationals for Nigeria where he has taken a five wicket bag and a hat- trick. He also played in the 2020 Under-19 Cricket World Cup in South Africa. ==Other websites== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian cricketers
